Application Requirements

I want to be able to generate an email with the following syntax:
'filename.lastname@department.company.com'

I want to be able to determine the relevent department, and if none then leave blank

Generate a random String for a password

Use setters to change the password, set mailbox capacity and define alternate email address

Use getters to display name, email, and mailbox capacity

Implement File handling methods to store data into .txt file